      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ZABDON JUSTICE (1) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing fifth (19.18) in a Grade 5 at this track. Solid record here winning three races. Better than the latest effort and deserves another chance. RAINMAKER JOE (4) rocketed out of the inside draw with a strong early sectional and gave a sight but had to settle for a placing, finishing second (19.69) at Q Lakeside over 352m. Expected to be in the finish again. NOAKI WARRIOR (2) had a tricky draw last time and although midfield in fourth wasn't far away finishing 3.5 lengths from the winner (16.81). Has ability and a bold showing is expected. AGILE BOY (8) is in the mix despite missing out at this track last time.",
